Code preview of the table BC_展位异动方案主表

alter table "BC_BoothChange"
drop constraint FK_BC_BOOTH_REFERENCE_BC_CHANG;

drop table "BC_BoothChange" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_BoothChange" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_BoothChange"
(
BCID NUMBER(32) not null,
"ShopMallID" NUMBER(32),
"MuseumID" NUMBER(32),
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32),
"ChangeTypeID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothTypeID" NUMBER(32),
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"StatusCode" INTEGER,
"ChangeRemark" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"UserID" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyUserID" NUMBER(32),
"ChangeTypeSubCode" NUMBER(32),
"SonStatusCode" INTEGER,
"IsEffect" INTEGER,
"WFFlowCode" VARCHAR2(50),
constraint PK_BC_BOOTHCHANGE primary key (BCID)
);

comment on column "BC_BoothChange"."ChangeTypeID" is
'10:空间调整、
20:内部调整、
30:进撤场、
40:变更经销商、
50:主数据变更、
60:子品牌系列变更
70：展位新增
80：展位移除
90:空间调整子流程';

comment on column "BC_BoothChange"."StatusCode" is
'10:草稿、
20:已创建、
30:已提交审批、
40:已审批完成、
50:方案废除
60:方案拒绝
70:方案退回(允许编辑)
80:方案撤销

';

comment on column "BC_BoothChange"."ChangeRemark" is
'空间调整备注、内部调整备注、进撤场备注、经销商变更备注、子品牌系列变更备注';

comment on column "BC_BoothChange"."SonStatusCode" is
'10:草稿、
20:已创建、
30:已提交审批、
40:已审批完成、
50:方案废除
60:方案拒绝
70:方案退回(允许编辑)
80:方案撤销
';

alter table "BC_BoothChange"
add constraint FK_BC_BOOTH_REFERENCE_BC_CHANG foreign key ("ChangeTypeID")
references "BC_ChangeTypeDictionary" ("TypeID");
